<!DOCTYPE html>

<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head runat="server">
    <title></title>
</head>
<body>
    <p><strong>List of Sites</strong></p>
<p>This screen will display the list of Sites along with their basic details such as the Organization they belong to, the number of Sensors configured on the Site, the name of the Deployment & Alert Technician and the current status of the Site</p>

<p>Click on the Sort Icons to sort the list</p>

 <p>You can customize the list of items displayed on the page by selecting the value from the records per page dropdown list </p>

<p>You can search for an item from the list by typing the search keyword in the Search text box</p>

<p>Click on the Add New Site button to add a new Site</p>

<p>Click on any of the Site Name to edit the particular Site</p>

<p>You can naviage between the list by using the navigation / paging buttons below the list</p>
</body>
</html>
